snippet.title: AQUAMAN 2 (2022) Teaser Trailer - Jason Momoa, Amber Heard
snippet.description:
AQUAMAN 2 (2022) Teaser Trailer - Jason Momoa, Amber Heard

Please Subscribe my Channel

Aquaman 2: The story of a soon-to-be king of the underwater kingdom of Atlantis, Arthur Curry, who has the power to speak to animals and control water. He’s also a part of the Justice League team. Directed by James Wan, this is a popular superhero movie from the DC Universe. The superb acting of Jason Momoa and other cast members attracted many fans and the movie became one of the highest-grossing DC films ever.
Now with more than 2 years since its release, there have been talks of a sequel for the film. Fans will be excited to know that Aquaman will be back with a sequel as Warner Bros released a teaser trailer of Aquaman 2 on Youtube.

Release date

Warner Bros. has planned to release the film on December 16, 2022, as confirmed in the teaser trailer of Aquaman 2. The premiere dates of upcoming DC films are always pre-planned. So the fans will have to wait a couple of years before Aquaman 2 is released. It will be marvelous as we’ll have more action from the superhero who can control the ocean and the aquatic life in it.

￼￼

Plot

The end-credits scene of Aquaman showed how David escapes and the way he plans to travel back to the Atlantis to have revenge on Arthur. As the kingdom of Arthur is in stakes it is likely the sequel of the film will show how he uses his mighty powers to save Atlantis and his family. Since he is the new king, he will have many responsibilities. New villains can also play a crucial role like mad scientist Dr. Stephen Shin who is out to search the lost kingdom of Atlantis.

Cast

The leading cast for Aquaman 2 are as follows –
Jason Momoa plays Arthur Curry/Aquaman, Amber Heard plays Mera, Willem Dafoe plays Nuidis Vulko and Patrick Wilson plays Orm
Marius/Ocean Master.
